data.description: Come take a look at this comfortable Mills Ranch two story home with lots of curb appeal. A large living area that flows into the sunny kitchen. A tall tiled breakfast bar to enjoy your breakfast separates the kitchen from the dining room and living room combination. Kitchen features all black appliances and plenty of cabinet space for all your cooking needs. The downstairs laundry rooms includes with a washer and dryer.  All bedrooms are located upstairs for your comfort.  Primary bedroom has a spacious walk in closet, and features an ensuite with oversized tub. Your backyard patio area fi perfect for family BBQ's and gatherings.  Detached 2 car garage with alley access for your private entry. Very clean home centrally located, close to schools and easy access to HWY 101.
